      <scopecontent id="aspace_97b44c73a6567212cac921a6518297af">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of clippings, records, scrapbooks, and photographs which document the students and operations of the Yale School of Forestry's (called the School of Forestry and Environmental Studies after 1972) training camps.</p>  
